<s> David Shaffer was named to the new post of executive vice president of the Maxwell Macmillan group of this communications giant . </s>
<s> Mr. Shaffer takes primary responsibility for the electronic and technical-services group . </s>
<s> He had been group vice president of the electronic-publishing group . </s>
<s> Also , Sheldon Aboff , formerly a vice president at Maxwell , was named group vice president with responsibility for various electronic and publishing-group companies . </s>
